        "Description": "you were tasked with killing three heads of the Italian opposition. Lorenzo, editor-in-chief of the opposition news agency, Forte, a popular speaker among young people, and Mulo, security officer for the head of the opposition-Marco Abiatti. All targets are in their homes and watching Marco&apos;s performance. The client wants you to eliminate them with a series of explosions, undermining the reputation of the Italian government in order to cause wave of indignation and start a revolution.",
